summary: Former Super Eagles striker Emmanuel Emenike shows off new house
title: Former Super Eagles striker Emmanuel Emenike shows off new house
body:
Former Super Eagles striker Emmanuel Emenike shows off new house

Emmanuel Emenike took to social media to celebrate his new home in Imo State.

Former Super Eagles striker Emmanuel Emenike has a new mansion in his hometown of Imo State.

Emenike who was on loan in the Spanish LaLiga with Las Palmas in 2018, where he suffered relegation has taken to social media to show off his new mansion reportedly worth millions of naira.

blog.name: earthstory
blog.title: The Earth Story
blog.description:
This is the blog homepage of the Facebook group "The Earth Story" (Click here to visit our Facebook group). “The Earth Story” are group of volunteers with backgrounds throughout the Earth Sciences. We cover all Earth sciences - oceanography, climatology, geology, geophysics and much, much more. Our articles combine the latest research, stunning photography, and basic knowledge of geosciences, and are written for everyone!

Winner of the award for Best Education Weblog in the 2015 bloggies


We hope you find us to be a unique home for learning about the Earth sciences, and we hope you enjoy!
